{"word":"ὄμφορα","slug":"ὄμφορα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n73969\" key=\"o)/mfora\" type=\"gloss\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὄμφορα·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅσα ἀπὸ τῶν ἱερῶν ἐκφέρεσθαι ὁ νόμος κωλύει,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀμφύνειν·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὔξειν, σεμνύνειν, ἐντιμότερον ποιεῖν,</foreign> Id., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author> </bibl> (Cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὤμφυναν.</foreign>) <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὁμῶλαξ</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ᾰκος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁμαῦλαξ</foreign> (q.v.).</entryFree>"}]}